# Shared blocked-path patterns for git hooks.
# Sourced by ~/.githooks/pre-commit and ~/.githooks/commit-msg.
# One ERE pattern per line. Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# These patterns are matched against:
#   - staged file paths (pre-commit file-name check)
#   - staged diff additions (pre-commit content check)
#   - commit message body (commit-msg check)

ai_scripts/
ai_docs/
ai_logs/
ai_temp/
ai_tests/
ai_issues/
ai_wiki/
\.claude/
AGENTS\.md
CLAUDE\.md
CLAUDE\.local\.md
